🎬 Step 1: Get Your TMDb API Key (Free & Best for this project)
TMDb is the best choice — it's free, has rich data (posters, ratings, genres, trending movies), and is widely used in real projects.
Follow these steps:

Go to 👉 https://www.themoviedb.org/signup
Create a free account & verify your email
Go to 👉 https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
Click "Create" → Choose "Developer"
Fill in the form:

App Name: Movie Search App
App URL: http://localhost:3000
Summary: A React learning project for searching and viewing movies


Submit → You'll get your API Key (v3 auth) — copy it!


